Class BotLotPFRandom

  • java.lang.Object
    • botLot.pathFinding.Algorithms.BotLotPFAlgorithm
      • botLot.pathFinding.Algorithms.BotLotPFRandom
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BotLotPFAlgInterface

    public class BotLotPFRandom
extends BotLotPFAlgorithm
implements BotLotPFAlgInterface
    Finds a path by randomly selecting edges on each node.

    Obviously not a great way to do this. Done for testing simple things. Or directing something for the scenic route.

    Started: 2/13/16

    TODO:: rewrite to ignore edges to avoid.

    Version:
    1.0 3/7/16
